title: 121: Mass Building Exercises & Polka Dot Shoes
description: What's with Adam's shoes? Maybe they are the key to his muscle building success. OR maybe it is just because he, Sal and Justin do special mass building exercises. Listen now to hear their analysis of the best exercises to put on size.
